Package: fin.extract
Title: Financial Statement Extraction Platform
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Jefferson", "Ndeke", , "jefferson@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Ingests PDF financial statements (native and scanned), extracts
    tabular data with a column-aware engine, and stores confirmed records in a
    Hive-partitioned Parquet lake indexed by a DuckDB control plane. Serves
    a catalog browser and trend visualizations over the saved store.
